    "8 Leveraging vortex beam propagation characteristics for enhanced environmental monitoring.",
    "As vortex beams propagate through the atmosphere, turbulence disrupts their intensity distribution and modifies their spiral phase structure, leading to the formation of speckle patterns and the dispersion of the OAM spectrum.",
